ca.mcgill.ecse211.team11

Class Initializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.team11.Initializer

  • public class Initializer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class bootstraps the robot by initializing every system.

    It initializes all the sensors and motors and handles the eventual exceptions that could arise. It also initializes all the robot's subsystems.
